{
  "stem": "16.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you heard what the Germans are-- this is already later on, when the Germans were promising you this-- that we're all taking you to one town somewhere in Hungary where all the Jews will be assembled in that one town.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so you'll meet your parents there at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just wanted to make my way back home to Munkacs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was about a year-- about a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hadn't been home at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they entered-- I think it was in March.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- but the directives that were issued maybe two weeks later-- all the Jews have to wear an arm band.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another week later, all the Jews have to wear a, a-- the Star, Star of David.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the Jews have to move to another part of town, which was the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed in or out of there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it just so happens I was allowed to go out because, as I said, I was printing for the Hungarian Army all kinds of papers that they needed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just several streets that were secluded, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't really know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that we had to go out in the middle of the street one day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in early May.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a few hours later, they loaded us onto boxcars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And three days later, I wound up in a prison camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just came around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and it wasn't even the, the, the Hungarian police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The gendarmes, they were the worst.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were worse than, than the Germans themselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They brought in police from different cities so that you don't know privately these people that you are dealing with right now, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were just terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Because they were--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
